{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4c435680-edd4-4176-977c-9ce0e0023578","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter entirely.** The test binary is now exclusively a Microsoft.Testing.Platform executable — it no longer ships the VSTest adapter DLLs that `vstest.console` needs to discover tests.\n\nIn 3.x you could set `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` to keep compatibility; that property is gone in 4.x.\n\n### How to fix your CI\n\nReplace `vstest.console` with either:\n\n1. **`dotnet test`** (recommended — it bridges to Microsoft.Testing.Platform automatically since .NET SDK 9+):\n   ```\n   dotnet test TestProject.csproj\n   ```\n\n2. **Run the test app directly** (it's a standalone executable now):\n   ```\n   dotnet run --project TestProject.csproj -- --report-trx\n   ```\n\nNo project file changes are needed — your `.csproj` and test code are already correct for 4.1.0.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"953751e8-edcc-43b0-991e-d4280f9700c4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user upgraded from MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0 to MSTest.Sdk/4.1.0 and vstest.console no longer discovers tests. This is a known breaking change.\n\nStarting with MSTest.Sdk 3.4+, the default test runner changed from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (the new \"Microsoft Testing Platform\" / \"MSTest runner\"). In MSTest.Sdk 3.x, there was a property `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` that could be set to opt back into VSTest compatibility. \n\nBut in MSTest.Sdk 4.x, VSTest support was completely removed. The `UseVSTest` property is no longer supported. The test executable is now a standalone executable that uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform natively, and it no longer produces the VSTest adapter assemblies needed for vstest.console to discover tests.\n \nThe solution is to migrate away from vstest.console entirely—either use `dotnet test` which works with both runners starting in .NET SDK 9+, or run the test executable directly with the appropriate flags to generate test reports.","outputTokens":594,"requestId":"0BC8:15632C:BF0112:DB3B0D:69F02444"},"id":"9a193c52-4115-4456-a05c-60c683e78228","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:06:57.497Z","parentId":"cba2efda-4751-41d6-b029-0158a72aeb5c"}
